episodes.title: Episode 86: Dinner for Vampires by Bethany Joy Lenz
episodes.description: On today’s episode, we’re reviewing the witty and dark memoir: Dinner for Vampires: by Bethany Joy Lenz. We’re all about nostalgia on this one.. Could a more perfect Haley James Scott exist?? And all while going through an absolute nightmare in her personal life. Tune in to hear us discuss the audacity of these cult leaders, the overwhelming amount of religion and, of course, the connections to a cult favorite TV show. CONTAINS SPOILERS Make sure to rate, review and subscribe to the podcast and follow us on TikTok and Instagram @fullybookedcaffpod. Thanks for listening!
